OL,3,C'Inherently unique': NI farmers hope
OL,4,CChancellor changes mind on inheritance
OL,5,Ctax
OL,7,FFarmers have urged the Chancellor to
OL,8,Fuse next week's budget to roll back on
OL,9,Fplans to change inheritance tax rules.
OL,11,FThousands of farms in Northern Ireland
OL,12,Fare set to be impacted by changes when
OL,13,Fthey come into effect next April.
OL,15,FRachel Reeves announced the reform at
OL,16,Flast year's budget.
