OL,3,C'Inherently unique': NI farmers hope
OL,4,CChancellor changes mind on inheritance
OL,5,Ctax
OL,7,FDespite a major protest at Westminster
OL,8,Fin the weeks after, farmers say they
OL,9,Fhave had no direct engagement with the
OL,10,FChancellor.
OL,12,FSam Hanna has been farming all his
OL,13,Flife, but like many other farms, his
OL,14,Fone is owned by his elderly father.
OL,16,FSam told UTV: "I'm a 51 year old
OL,17,Ffarmer and my dad is 78, everything is
OL,18,Fstill in his name. We are trying to
OL,19,Fget things transferred, we have been
OL,20,Fholding tight thinking it will never
OL,21,Fhappen."
