OL,7,FHe isn't confident the Chancellor will
OL,8,Fchange her position at next week's
OL,9,Fbudget.
OL,11,F"It would be too much of a tail
OL,12,Fbetween the legs and a u-turn. They
OL,13,Fare too proud to even consider it."
OL,15,FFarms were previously exempt from
OL,16,Finheritance tax but that is set to
OL,17,Fchange in April 2026.
