OL,7,FGoing forward under the reforms the
OL,8,Ffirst #1 million is tax free, but
OL,9,Fanything over that will be subjected
OL,10,Fto a 20% charge.
OL,12,FAnalysis shows that nearly half of
OL,13,Ffarms here will be impacted and many
OL,14,Fcould be forced to sell land to pay
OL,15,Fthe bill.
OL,17,FIn a last-ditch attempt, a delegation
OL,18,Ffrom Northern Ireland has travelled to
OL,19,FWestminster on Monday to lobby for
OL,20,Fchange.
