OL,7,F"The aim is for UFU staff and members
OL,8,Fto continue translating to MPs the
OL,9,Finherently unique nature of our family
OL,10,Ffarms here in Northern Ireland,
OL,11,Fcharacterised by high land values, an
OL,12,Folder demographic of farmers and
OL,13,Fprevalence of sole-owner livestock-
OL,14,Fbased farms, in a plead for government
OL,15,Fto urgently change course on their
OL,16,Fproposals before the upcoming Budget."
